item.name: API Redirects

response.name: Success

item.description:
Meraki recently changed its API base hostname from dashboard.meraki.com to api.meraki.com

All other URL components remain intact. The legacy "dashboard" option still works but an
HTTP 307 redirect is returned. Postman automatically follows them (which can be disabled),
which is demonstrated in this folder.
